This paper deals with the problem of reasoning over time in knowledge graphs, which involves machine learning, natural language processing, and database systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DB (Databases), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
